com.nokia.maps.kml

Interface IconStyle

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ColorStyle

    public interface IconStyle
extends ColorStyle
    This interface represents the <IconStyle> tag from KML specification. Specifies how icons for point <Placemark> elements are drawn. The <Icon> element specifies the icon image. The <hotSpot> element specifies the position within the Icon that is "anchored"

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      static java.lang.String ELEMENT
      This constant indicates the <IconStyle> as an XML element.
      static java.lang.String SCALE
      This constant an XML attribute to enlarge/reduce the size of the image associated with this Icon.
